snippet: Survivors of a plane crash are dying in “36 Saints,” and two detectives try to stop the apparently supernatural forces behind the killings.
abstract: Andy Webster reviews movie 36 Saints, directed by Eddy Duran and starring Franky G.
lead_paragraph: Survivors of a plane crash are dying in “36 Saints,” and two detectives try to stop the apparently supernatural forces behind the killings.

headline.seo: ‘36 Saints’ Pits City Cops Against Biblical Forces
